@page "/"

<PageTitle>Newsroom Control Center</PageTitle>

<h1 class="display-4">Editor-in-Chief Control Center</h1>
<p class="lead">Configure coverage priorities, follow live orchestration runs, and monitor business performance.</p>

<div class="row g-4">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">Coverage Priorities</div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Define upcoming beats, embargoes, and story angles for autonomous agents.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Pitch board with directive templates</li>
                    <li>Embargo calendar synced to Azure Service Bus topics</li>
                    <li>Policy toggles for sustainability, politics, and investigations</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">Workflow Monitor</div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Observe state transitions across <code>StoryStage</code> values generated by orchestrated agents.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Live message stream from Dapr/Service Bus</li>
                    <li>Manual override &amp; escalation buttons</li>
                    <li>Durable Functions history with correlation IDs</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row g-4 mt-1">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">Paywall &amp; Monetization</div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Tailor MonetizationAgent rules by desk, keyword, and subscriber cohort.</p>
                <p>Integrates with Azure App Configuration and Azure Key Vault for secure rule storage.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">SEO &amp; Distribution</div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Preview metadata, JSON-LD, and cross-channel messaging generated by SEOPackaging and Distribution agents.</p>
                <p>Surface suggestions powered by Azure OpenAI.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">Analytics Snapshot</div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Real-time KPIs pulled from AnalyticsAgent, Application Insights, and Cosmos DB.</p>
                <p>Trigger A/B experiments and subscription funnels directly from this portal.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
